sequenceDiagram
  participant Log as EventLogStore
  participant Worker as FeatureStoreIngestLauncher
  participant CB as CircuitBreaker
  participant FS as FeatureStoreService
  participant DLQ as DeadLetterQueue
  Log-->>Worker: read batch for tenant offset
  Worker->>Worker: extract ML features
  Worker->>CB: guarded write
  CB->>FS: persist features
  FS-->>CB: success/failure
  alt success
    CB-->>Worker: ok
    Worker->>Worker: advance tenant offset
  else permanent failure
    CB-->>Worker: error/open circuit
    Worker->>DLQ: store failed entry
  end

